			"id": "d110d55b-3fcc-46a0-97b3-da27cb6929ec",
			"description": "## What is Data Kiosk?\n\n[Data Kiosk](https://developer-docs.amazon.com/sp-api/docs/data-kiosk-api-v2023-11-15-reference) is a GraphQL-based API that lets you query analytics data from Amazon. Instead of requesting pre-defined report types, you write queries to pull exactly the data you need.\n\n## How This Flow Works\n\nThis folder walks you through the full lifecycle of a Data Kiosk query:\n\n1. **Create a new query** — Submit a GraphQL query to Data Kiosk.\n    \n2. **Check query status** — Poll until the query finishes processing.\n    \n3. **Get document details** — Retrieve the document URL for the completed query.\n    \n4. **Download document content** — Fetch the actual report data.\n    \n\n📘 Learn more: [Data Kiosk API Use Case Guide](https://developer-docs.amazon.com/sp-api/docs/data-kiosk-api-v2023-11-15-use-case-guide)",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "prerequest",
					"script": {
						"type": "text/javascript",
						"packages": {},
						"requests": {},
						"exec": [
							"pm.sendRequest({",
							"    url: pm.environment.get(\"oauth_url\"),",
							"    method: 'POST',",
							"    header: {",
							"        'content-type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded',",
							"        'Accept': 'application/json'",
							"    },",
							"    body: {",
							"        mode: 'urlencoded',",
							"        urlencoded: [",
							"            {key: \"grant_type\", value: \"refresh_token\", disabled: false},",
							"            {key: \"refresh_token\", value: pm.environment.get(\"refresh_token\"), disabled: false},",
							"            {key: \"client_id\", value: pm.environment.get(\"client_id\"), disabled: false},",
							"            {key: \"client_secret\", value: pm.environment.get(\"client_secret\"), disabled: false}",
							"        ]",
							"    }",
							"}, function (err, res) {",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"access_token\", res.json().access_token);",
							"});"
						],
						"id": "09e3f24e-1e25-47e5-a5e9-e8e3795b4815"
					}
				},
